      <section eId="sec_2852">
        <num>2852</num>
        <heading>Senate confirmation of certain chief executive officers</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_2852__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>of section one thousand\ntwenty-f of this chapter the senate shall vote to confirm any such\nappointment within sixty days of its submission to the senate during\nsession, or if such submission is made when the senate is not in\nsession, within seven days of the convening for session. If the senate\nfails to vote to confirm any such appointment within the time prescribed\nin this section, such appointment shall be deemed confirmed without any\nfurther action by the senate.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
